WINDOWS1       Administrators TESTLAB\Dom... S-1-5-21-89...           True           True
WINDOWS1       Administrators TESTLAB\har... S-1-5-21-89...          False           True

.EXAMPLE

Get-NetLocalGroup | Get-NetLocalGroupMember | ft

